'''Mantle'''是一个由[[AMD|AMD]]主导开发的<ref name="Dave Altavilla" />面向3D游戏的[[彩現|图形渲染]] [[应用程序接口|API]]，开发从2013年开始，并在[[DICE|DICE]]的帮助下进行，於2013年9月25日發布。<ref name="whitepaper">{{cite web |url= http://www.amd.com/Documents/Mantle_White_Paper.pdf |title= Mantle WhitePaper |format= pdf |publisher= [[Advanced_Micro_Devices|AMD]] |accessdate= 2016-03-21 |archive-date= 2019-06-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190611114759/https://www.amd.com/Documents/Mantle_White_Paper.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref>尽管[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]配置的GPU也支持Mantle，Mantle作为[[Direct3D|Direct3D]]和[[OpenGL|OpenGL]]的补充，主要用于[[个人电脑|PC]]。<ref name="Dave Altavilla" /><ref name="tomshardware">
{{cite web |last=Parrish |first=Kevin |title=AMD's Mantle API Gives Devs Direct Hardware Control |url=http://www.tomshardware.com/news/amd-mantle-api-gcn-battlefield-4,24418.html |work=tomshardware.com |publisher=Tom's Hardware |accessdate=Oct 1, 2013|date=Sep 25, 2013}}</ref>

AMD在2015年3月表示，由于与之类似的[[Vulkan_(API)|Vulkan]]已经可以取代Mantle在游戏工业的作用，公司将未来逐步的将重心从Mantle转移至其他领域。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://community.amd.com/community/amd-blogs/amd-gaming/blog/2015/03/03/one-of-mantles-futures-vulkan|title= One of Mantle's Futures: Vulkan | AMD Blogs|accessdate= 2016-03-21|archive-date= 2015-03-06|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150306190250/http://community.amd.com/community/amd-blogs/amd-gaming/blog/2015/03/03/one-of-mantles-futures-vulkan|dead-url= yes}}</ref>未来两年AMD仍将提供驱动支持，不过直到2015年3月，Mantle API本身并没有公开。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.anandtech.com/show/9095/amd-mantle-api-programming-guide-available|title= AMD Mantle API Programming Guide Available|accessdate= 2015-03-22|archive-date= 2020-11-08|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201108090829/https://www.anandtech.com/show/9095/amd-mantle-api-programming-guide-available|dead-url= no}}</ref>

Mantle API僅支持基於 GCN 架構的顯卡和 APU  ，而不支持基於 TeraScale 架構的顯卡和 APU。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Understanding AMD’s Mantle: A Low-Level Graphics API For GCN|url=https://www.anandtech.com/show/7371/understanding-amds-mantle-a-lowlevel-graphics-api-for-gcn|access-date=2021-12-17|last=Smith|first=Ryan|work=www.anandtech.com|archive-date=2022-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220509084449/https://www.anandtech.com/show/7371/understanding-amds-mantle-a-lowlevel-graphics-api-for-gcn}}</ref>

